{
  "texts": [
    "As they explained, these voices appeared to be warm and healing: \"those comforting and encouraging words from that kind of voice deeply touched me. \"",
    "P1 always chose the \"lazy goat\" (a popular cartoon character in China) for their beloved digital dog, highlighting that its voice made them feel \"relaxed after a busy day. \"",
    "P6 and P9 preferred the chatbot to speak with their hometown accent, noting that hearing a familiar voice made them \"open up more easily, and feel I could freely express my innermost thoughts\" (P6).In avatar choices, participants tended to use cheerful and cute emojis for supportive personas.",
    "For instance, P19 used (a smiling face with hearts) for the gentle listener chatbot's avatar to gain positive energy after a tough day.",
    "They explained that the cute avatar \"makes the conversation more pleasant and enjoyable.\""
  ]
}